      "question": "Why is it important to acknowledge all exclusions from forests-related data disclosure every year?",
      "answer": "It is important to acknowledge all exclusions from forests-related data disclosure every year to enhance transparency, despite disclosure of the same exclusion in previous years, to ensure all data users are always aware of what data has been included in the response."
