      "answer": "Report on the level of traceability of embedded soy, including whether you can trace to the soy production origin, the soy feed supplier origin, or the origin of the animal that was fed the soy. If traced back to the soy production origin, indicate if this is to country/area level, sourcing area, or production unit. Provide details of the methods and tools used to trace embedded soy."
    },
